### Check existing account in Supabase
GET https://jpfxxoflclkpqsibvdil.supabase.co/rest/v1/accounts?id=eq.{{accountId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{supabase_service_key}}

### Create new account in Supabase
POST https://jpfxxoflclkpqsibvdil.supabase.co/rest/v1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{supabase_service_key}}
Prefer: return=representation

{
  "id": "{{accountId}}",
  "unipile_account_id": "{{accountId}}",
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "name": "LinkedIn",
  "status": "Ativo",
  "initials": "LI"
}

### Update existing account status
PATCH https://jpfxxoflclkpqsibvdil.supabase.co/rest/v1/accounts?id=eq.{{accountId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{supabase_service_key}}

{
  "status": "Ativo"
}
